She rolls to the Forest she meets a friend.  A life size Gummy Bear peaks from around the tree and joins on her journey.  They soon hear a rustling up ahead in the trees. The Gummy Runs ahead thinking its his friend.  Furiosa rides to protect her friend and the two are surprised to see an Alien standing in front of them. The Alien jumps on the Gummy Bear and eats it, getting stuck in the GOO, giving Furiosa a chance to arm herself or run.
To Live: She drives away
To Die: she uses the shotgun and gets sprayed by acid
To Die: she tries to save her friend and gets sliced in half by the tail
